product.name: Muslogy for CR-V 2025 2024 2023 Trunk Cargo Cover Retractable Rear Trunk Security Cover Shield Shade Compatible with 6th Generation Honda CRV and CRV Hybrid 2023+
product.description:
Our team aims to create a reliable one-stop shop for CR-V 2023 aftermarket products for every valuable CR-V owner.
Our team is committed to developing high quality and reliable CR-V 2023 accessories and continuously providing a superior shopping experience to ensure that every Muslogy customer is satisfied.
product.bullet_points:
• Perfect Fitment: Designed according to 3D laser scanning data to make sure it fits your CR-V perfectly. Shaped to fit the contour of the trunk and can be installed perfectly in your trunk.
• High-Quality Material: The cargo cover is made of high-strength material and there is Flannel attached on both sides to protect your trunk from scratches while install and make it noise-free. Our Smooth knob surface won't damage your trunk surface.
• Function: Protect your valuables and personal privacy in the trunk from peeking and prevent your items from UV rays even in hot summer.
• Easy to install: No tools needed. Simply insert the bar into the groove before pulling out the cargo cover, and then snap in the buckles on both sides to secure the cargo cover in place.
• Service: We dedicated to providing you great products and shopping experience. Feel free to contact us if there is any problem any time.
